{"tid":1485060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英接受FOX訪問：美國應助港人抗爭","createTime":"2019-08-18T15:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:46:42.000Z","uid":227801,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"905dd2e0ee91d5eaa5b98b4b5f7f84a8d8e9d034","tid":1485060,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:27:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190818/59946557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190818%2F59946557&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cdRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=3991f226\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190818%2F59946557&h=2a989e17\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190818/59946557</a><br />\n壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英香港時間周日晚上10時許接受美國霍士新聞（Fox News）新聞頻道節目《Sunday Morning Futures with Maria Bartiromo》訪問，讚好美國總統特朗普將「反送中」示威與中美貿易戰掛勾，因為現時香港示威人士爭取的「自由、民主」，正是美國及香港一直堅持的核心價值，大家都正參與「同一場自由之戰」，因此美國應該幫助香港示威人士的抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英讚賞特朗普將香港的運動與中美貿易戰掛勾，更指港人目前致力保衞的自由及核心價值，正正就是美國一直爭取、堅持的同一價值觀，因此香港與美國正在打同一場戰爭，故希望美國可以幫助港人。<br />\n<br />\n主持人詢問黎智英，今天滂沱大雨，為何港人仍無懼風雨參加遊行？黎智英回答因為港人仍未爭取到真普選，一日未實現真普選，<br />\n香港的自由就會慢慢被中共蠶食。而且港人亦明白，如果《逃犯條例》修訂案通過，香港便會完蛋，金融體系會崩潰。<br />\n因此大家都致力對抗中共的獨裁主義，一直爭取政府回應五大訴求，因為香港能取得今天的成功，正因與中國具有不同的價值觀，因此港人必須保護這些核心價值。被問到中共指美國等西方國家在背後支持這場運動，黎智英強調根本不是事實，更指北京當局經常說謊，完全不足信。<br />\n<br />\n上'月黎智英亦曾亮相同一節目，批評已「壽終正寢」的《逃犯條例》修訂案會損害香港法治，令香港的國際金融中心地位不保，港人擔心核心價值受到威脅，故以激烈手段捍衞自由。<br />\n黎智英近期先後獲美國副總統彭斯（Mike Pence）、國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）和國家安全顧問博爾頓（John Bolton）以及多位參議員接見，<br />\n他認為，香港的抗爭等同美國正與中國進行的新冷戰，而香港猶如為美國深入「敵陣」作戰一樣，故美國有義務支持香港，而香港與西方擁有共同價值，每次港人抗爭但遭到打壓時，也提醒世界中國是不可信的。<br />\n美國霍士新聞頻道/《蘋果》資料室"},{"pid":"57e4ab6c9a55630818d3f845c6d23b8eedaf4a55","tid":1485060,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a05673df5a900100306d1e84384a6445e1f2562","tid":1485060,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e857e457459891e2aa58a016bb8c84401f27638","tid":1485060,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cf89862f72103519ed6fcfe1aa0800c458be60","tid":1485060,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:53:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不割蓆 不分化 核爆都唔割</span>"},{"pid":"2e4015a5fd93575aa426b35e61a6284353cac57e","tid":1485060,"uid":40356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T15:59:01.000Z","msg":"多謝肥佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4e231bb841a17cc150160cbaf5ab9560bbcc92","tid":1485060,"uid":82853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"trump trump個愛台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d753ed21f12bcf9ee78214cddca839cf4890f1e","tid":1485060,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"又話核彈都唔割？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1484962\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1484962</a>"},{"pid":"4d87a46b33bca29c6eb40bcbc8bc6ed7140aff0c","tid":1485060,"uid":68746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:02:41.000Z","msg":"係做到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd33ffc2592815b756d486adf3403ad47c615ef6","tid":1485060,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d4e231bb841a17cc150160cbaf5ab9560bbcc92","tid":1485060,"uid":82853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:00:04.000Z","msg":"trump trump個愛台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"黎智英之前仲親自見Mike Pence<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190709/large/1562644999_586f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190709%2Flarge%2F1562644999_586f.jpg&h=928e33c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"379e56df1426d7c78fc266fa07f969e48a6cb37f","tid":1485060,"uid":210280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:46:42.000Z","msg":"Sir this way"}]}